{"tid":564803,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Pixel 2 系列出現機身升溫、續航力驟降問題","createTime":"2018-02-18T11:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T12:39:22.000Z","uid":23677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bbdd6dc7fec480968ef2adad080dbc940a25c850","tid":564803,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T11:16:12.000Z","msg":"Google Pixel 2 系列手機自推出以來，雖然獲得不少好評，但也一直風波不斷。據 9to5Google 引述 Reddit 討論區和 Google 的 Pixel 使用者社群的討論，不少使用者手上的 Pixel 2 和 Pixel 2 XL 都在安裝 Google 釋出的 2 月安全性更新後，出現不同的問題。9to5Google 的 Ben Schoon 自己也發現所用的 Pixel 2 XL 在待機模式時機身明顯升溫，而且續航力明顯減少。<br />\n據使用者的回報，並非所有 Pixel 2 手機都會同時出現以上兩個問題，有的則是耗電量不穩定。但手機有出現問題的使用者，都表示他們安裝了本月的安全性更新後就開始出現症狀。雖然目前未能下定論，但似乎也與這安全性更新跑不了關係。<br />\n<br />\n我們已經向 Google 查詢有關消息，並等待他們的回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/02/18/google-pixel-2-warming-shortened-battery-life/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2Fgoogle-pixel-2-warming-shortened-battery-life%2F&d=O8fQufEf9OSvJRPhvPNUaTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=8feb25b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/02/18/google-pixel-2-warming-shortened-battery-life/</a>"},{"pid":"c1f218da022f258917981716dd86c663763503bc","tid":564803,"uid":134032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"我又唔覺有問題"},{"pid":"294689a2dd9cdc709956d4d0d6f19a92b1e5f20f","tid":564803,"uid":23677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c1f218da022f258917981716dd86c663763503bc","tid":564803,"uid":134032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"我又唔覺有問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T12:04:25.000Z","msg":"但我覺呢排食電左"},{"pid":"4cb34a3035e3d71359c4406e5d579d26cfd8eb5d","tid":564803,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T12:07:01.000Z","msg":"AI排毒"},{"pid":"a7c5701336fc6f3704ee78de09853239ed1442af","tid":564803,"uid":17604,"like":0,"di